    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## INPUT – Fetch Video Topic\n\n**Purpose**:\nGets the next row from Google Sheets that is marked for production.\n\n**What to do**:\nAdd new ideas in the sheet → set production = for production.\nThe workflow will automatically pick the next one and begin generating scenes.",
        "height": 288,
        "width": 656
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -400,
        800
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "e3bdd20c-f9fc-490f-8dd7-bb9268b7e525",
      "name": "Sticky Note4"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Generate Scene Titles\n\n**Purpose**:\nCreates 5 concise POV action prompts that represent a “day in the life” sequence for your selected idea.\n\n**What to know**:\n\nUses your custom instructions to generate cinematic, action-heavy POV prompts.\n\nThese titles are later expanded into long descriptive prompts for image generation.",
        "height": 288,
        "width": 656
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -400,
        1504
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "308febce-c14f-4f00-8d5d-8947edcf3354",
      "name": "Sticky Note5"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Generate Prompts\n\n**Purpose**:\nTakes each short prompt and expands it into a detailed POV description optimized for Flux/MidJourney-style image generation.\n\n**What to know**:\n\nAlways includes first-person hands or limbs\n\nAdds environment descriptions from the sheet\n\nOutputs cinematic single-sentence prompts ready for text-to-image",
        "height": 304,
        "width": 544
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        336,
        112
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "56c4de2d-9c4c-4769-9688-e5364b4a5878",
      "name": "Sticky Note6"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Generate Images\n\n**Purpose**:\nUses PiAPI text-to-image to create 5 portrait-style POV images.\n\n**What to know**:\n\nEach image is generated from the expanded prompt\n\nWaits for the generation to complete\n\nThese images will be used as starting frames for video generation",
        "height": 272,
        "width": 544
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        336,
        448
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "a57647ec-9136-4d89-a5a9-6e925710b500",
      "name": "Sticky Note7"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Generate Videos\n\n**Purpose**:\nConverts each generated image into a 5-second cinematic POV video.\n\n**What to know**:\n\nUses Kling via PiAPI\n\nWaits for full processing\n\nProduces 5 short video clips used in the final compilation",
        "height": 288,
        "width": 544
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        336,
        1744
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "0c72155e-fdb3-4c7e-a0c7-f3eb10d3aa9d",
      "name": "Sticky Note8"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Generate Sounds\n\n**Purpose**:\nCreates ambient soundtracks for each scene using ElevenLabs audio generation.\n\n**What to know**:\n\nSound is based on the idea + scene action\n\nAudio is uploaded automatically to Google Drive\n\nPublic links are generated for Creatomate",
        "height": 304,
        "width": 544
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        336,
        2064
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "9963dfd0-a990-4ead-b658-5f1a92189576",
      "name": "Sticky Note9"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Merge & Compile Elements\n\n**Purpose**:\nCombines:\n✔ 5 scene titles\n✔ 5 video URLs\n✔ 5 sound URLs\n\ninto one structured JSON object used for rendering the final video.",
        "height": 240,
        "width": 656
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        944,
        832
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "d4bf8a1f-0190-4740-9d82-fd617d4e07de",
      "name": "Sticky Note12"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Render Final Video (Creatomate)\n\n**Purpose**:\nCreates 1 polished final video using your Creatomate template.\n\n**What to know**:\n\nInjects videos, sounds & titles into template layers\n\nReturns a final video download link\n\nUpdates your Google Sheet with the result",
        "height": 272,
        "width": 656
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        944,
        1488
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "7364ed37-703d-48a6-9c28-fd222531d8c6",
      "name": "Sticky Note15"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Update Sheet with Final Link\n\n**Purpose**:\nWrites back the final video link, marks the idea as done, and moves it to the publishing stage.",
        "width": 592
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1632,
        912
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "e91bd0af-31c5-4330-9c4a-d81353501e9f",
      "name": "Sticky Note16"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Publishing Agent\n\n**Purpose**:\nRuns separately on a different schedule.\nIt picks rows marked for publishing and uploads the final video to YouTube.\n\n**What to know**:\n\nDownloads video file\n\nUploads to YouTube with title & caption from the sheet\n\nSets video privacy to unlisted\n\nAfter upload, you can manually mark the row as complete",
        "height": 336,
        "width": 592
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1632,
        1488
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "2fa018d4-8c5d-451c-94d1-55ca5456ae29",
      "name": "Sticky Note17"
    }
